Author: phmwls
Text: It’d be best to talk to a psychologist to see what might be going on.  If you’re looking for tips on how to get healthier eating habits - you mentioned looking in the fridge or eating cookies, maybe meal prepping would help and setting a schedule until you develop an appetite.

Author: frogfacewheeler
Text: i don’t think it’s right for anyone to diagnose you over the internet without having met you or had a conversation with you. have you considered visiting a psychologist or getting help elsewhere?
